# в”Ђв”Ђ SI Base Units в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ

def "si:unit:metre" "SI base unit of length. Defined by fixing the speed of light c = 299,792,458 m/s exactly."
al si:unit:metre si:unit:meter
ln si:unit:metre si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:kilogram" "SI base unit of mass. Defined by fixing the Planck constant h = 6.62607015Г—10вЃ»ВівЃґ JВ·s exactly."
ln si:unit:kilogram si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:second" "SI base unit of time. Defined by 9,192,631,770 cycles of the Cs-133 ground-state hyperfine transition."
ln si:unit:second si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:ampere" "SI base unit of electric current. Defined by fixing the elementary charge e = 1.602176634Г—10вЃ»В№вЃ№ C exactly."
ln si:unit:ampere si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:kelvin" "SI base unit of thermodynamic temperature. Defined by fixing the Boltzmann constant k = 1.380649Г—10вЃ»ВІВі J/K exactly."
ln si:unit:kelvin si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:mole" "SI base unit of amount of substance. Defined by fixing the Avogadro constant Nв‚ђ = 6.02214076Г—10ВІВі molвЃ»В№ exactly."
ln si:unit:mole si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:candela" "SI base unit of luminous intensity. Defined by fixing the luminous efficacy Kcd = 683 lm/W at 540 THz exactly."
ln si:unit:candela si:unit sys:part_of

# в”Ђв”Ђ SI Derived Units (named) в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ

def "si:unit:radian" "SI unit of plane angle. Dimensionless (m/m). 2ПЂ rad = full circle."
al si:unit:radian si:unit:rad
ln si:unit:radian si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:steradian" "SI unit of solid angle. Dimensionless (mВІ/mВІ). 4ПЂ sr = full sphere."
al si:unit:steradian si:unit:sr
ln si:unit:steradian si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:hertz" "SI unit of frequency. 1 Hz = 1 sвЃ»В№ (cycles per second)."
al si:unit:hertz si:unit:hz
ln si:unit:hertz si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:newton" "SI unit of force. 1 N = 1 kgв‹…mв‹…sвЃ»ВІ. Named after Isaac Newton."
al si:unit:newton si:unit:n
ln si:unit:newton si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:pascal" "SI unit of pressure and stress. 1 Pa = 1 N/mВІ = 1 kgв‹…mвЃ»В№в‹…sвЃ»ВІ."
al si:unit:pascal si:unit:pa
ln si:unit:pascal si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:joule" "SI unit of energy, work, and heat. 1 J = 1 Nв‹…m = 1 kgв‹…mВІв‹…sвЃ»ВІ."
al si:unit:joule si:unit:j
ln si:unit:joule si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:watt" "SI unit of power (rate of energy transfer). 1 W = 1 J/s = 1 kgв‹…mВІв‹…sвЃ»Ві."
al si:unit:watt si:unit:w
ln si:unit:watt si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:coulomb" "SI unit of electric charge. 1 C = 1 Aв‹…s. Approximately 6.242Г—10В№вЃё elementary charges."
al si:unit:coulomb si:unit:c
ln si:unit:coulomb si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:volt" "SI unit of electric potential difference (EMF). 1 V = 1 J/C = 1 kgв‹…mВІв‹…sвЃ»Вів‹…AвЃ»В№."
al si:unit:volt si:unit:v
ln si:unit:volt si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:farad" "SI unit of electrical capacitance. 1 F = 1 C/V = 1 kgвЃ»В№в‹…mвЃ»ВІв‹…sвЃґв‹…AВІ."
al si:unit:farad si:unit:f
ln si:unit:farad si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:ohm" "SI unit of electrical resistance. 1 О© = 1 V/A = 1 kgв‹…mВІв‹…sвЃ»Вів‹…AвЃ»ВІ."
al si:unit:ohm si:unit:ohm_symbol
ln si:unit:ohm si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:siemens" "SI unit of electrical conductance (reciprocal of ohm). 1 S = 1 A/V = 1 kgвЃ»В№в‹…mвЃ»ВІв‹…sВів‹…AВІ."
al si:unit:siemens si:unit:s_conductance
ln si:unit:siemens si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:weber" "SI unit of magnetic flux. 1 Wb = 1 Vв‹…s = 1 kgв‹…mВІв‹…sвЃ»ВІв‹…AвЃ»В№."
al si:unit:weber si:unit:wb
ln si:unit:weber si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:tesla" "SI unit of magnetic flux density (magnetic field strength). 1 T = 1 Wb/mВІ = 1 kgв‹…sвЃ»ВІв‹…AвЃ»В№."
al si:unit:tesla si:unit:t_field
ln si:unit:tesla si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:henry" "SI unit of electrical inductance. 1 H = 1 Wb/A = 1 kgв‹…mВІв‹…sвЃ»ВІв‹…AвЃ»ВІ."
al si:unit:henry si:unit:h_inductance
ln si:unit:henry si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:lumen" "SI unit of luminous flux. 1 lm = 1 cdв‹…sr."
al si:unit:lumen si:unit:lm
ln si:unit:lumen si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:lux" "SI unit of illuminance (luminous flux per unit area). 1 lx = 1 lm/mВІ."
al si:unit:lux si:unit:lx
ln si:unit:lux si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:becquerel" "SI unit of radioactivity. 1 Bq = 1 sвЃ»В№ (one nuclear decay per second)."
al si:unit:becquerel si:unit:bq
ln si:unit:becquerel si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:gray" "SI unit of absorbed ionising radiation dose. 1 Gy = 1 J/kg = 1 mВІв‹…sвЃ»ВІ."
al si:unit:gray si:unit:gy
ln si:unit:gray si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:sievert" "SI unit of ionising radiation dose equivalent (weighted by biological effect). 1 Sv = 1 J/kg."
al si:unit:sievert si:unit:sv
ln si:unit:sievert si:unit sys:part_of

def "si:unit:katal" "SI unit of catalytic activity. 1 kat = 1 molв‹…sвЃ»В№ (moles of substrate converted per second)."
al si:unit:katal si:unit:kat
ln si:unit:katal si:unit sys:part_of

