def "phys:const:mn" "Neutron rest mass. mв‚™ = 1.67492749804Г—10вЃ»ВІвЃ· kg = 939.56542052 MeV/cВІ."
al phys:const:mn phys:const:neutron_mass
ln phys:const:mn phys:const sys:part_of

def "phys:const:u" "Unified atomic mass unit (dalton). u = 1.66053906660Г—10вЃ»ВІвЃ· kg = 931.49410242 MeV/cВІ."
al phys:const:u phys:const:atomic_mass_unit
al phys:const:u phys:const:dalton
ln phys:const:u phys:const sys:part_of

def "phys:const:r" "Molar gas constant. R = Nв‚ђ k = 8.314462618 Jв‹…molвЃ»В№в‹…KвЃ»В№."
